						<p>On the north wall, central shrine, Umā Mahēśvara temple.</p>						

						<p><hi rend="bold">Year 6: 977 A.D.</hi></p>						

						<p>Records a gift of land by Eḻiṉūr-kiḻavaṉ after purchase for burning a perpetual lamp to Ādityēśvaram-uḍaiya-Mahādēva in Tirunallam.</p>						

